videos.description: American's Sa'eed Nelson sprints to the basket from the 3-point line and puts the moves on for the beautiful lay-in.
videos.headline: Nelson with the nifty lay-in

videos.description: Daxter Miles Jr. takes the pass from Jevon Carter on the fast break and makes an acrobatic finish.
videos.headline: Carter finds Miles Jr. for slick layup

videos.description: Larry Motuzis takes the pass off a screen and drains a 3-pointer from deep to close the gap on West Virginia's lead.
videos.headline: Motuzis drains an impressive deep three

videos.description: James Bolden takes the pass from  Daxter Miles Jr. and hits the shot despite being hit hard by the defender.
videos.headline: Bolden hits layup through hard foul

videos.description: Jevon Carter takes the ball in from half court, puts the moves on, leaps, and hits the difficult left-handed and-1.
videos.headline: Carter hits the ridiculous and-1

videos.description: Sam Iorio finds Larry Motuzis who leaps and hits the finger roll.
videos.headline: Motuzis hits the finger roll

videos.description: James Bolden puts the moves on and jukes the defender, then steps back for a clean 3-point jumper.
videos.headline: James Bolden hits the step-back three
